	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So we have up to a 250-segment liquid crystal display. Make an indexed-color image the size of the display, and have the value of each pixel represent which segment it belongs to. Then use palette animation to turn each segment on or off.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


